{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"cdbfce0722","title":"给曹云芳的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a0b0c6404c","index":0,"year":1956,"month":8,"day":11,"articleId":"cdbfce0722"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji36","name":"毛泽东全集第36卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/36-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji36":{"comments":[{"id":"1f963bbe91","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"cdbfce0722","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"曹云芳，原是罗哲烈士之妻。大革命时期曾随罗哲一起在毛泽东领导下做革命工作。"},{"id":"4c5b1cdac8","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"cdbfce0722","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"罗哲，中国共产党党员。大革命时期曾随毛泽东从事农民运动。1928年辆性。"}],"contents":[{"id":"b69eccfd8d","type":"title","text":"给曹云芳的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"cdbfce0722"},{"id":"1f963bbe91","type":"paragraph","text":"云芳同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"cdbfce0722"},{"id":"4c5b1cdac8","type":"paragraph","text":"七月八日的信收到，甚感。罗哲以同志英勇轴性，早就听到一些消息。一九四五年在重庆的时候，见到张维兄，曾打听你们的下落，他只告知你姐姐王夫人已故，你的情形他不知道。现知你仍健在，并有两个女儿能继承罗哲遗志，我很高兴。罗哲为党限苦工作，我可作证，当时没有别的证件。恤金由谁领的问题，应由当地政府去作决定，如果决定给继子，不给女儿，也就算了，不必为此去争论。攻墓可由家属修理。现寄上三百元，请你的量处理。今后如果还有困难，可以告我设法。你见过的两个孩子，一个在战争中栖性了，一个也已病废。你们在贵阳工作有成绩，向你们致贺","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"cdbfce0722"},{"id":"0bdaedeafa","type":"paragraph","text":"顺祝康吉","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"cdbfce0722"},{"id":"78abd56b0f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"cdbfce0722"},{"id":"2c89e87906","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五六年八月十一日","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"cdbfce0722"}],"page":{"id":"7aafc9db8d","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"cdbfce0722","start":448,"end":448}}}},"__N_SSG":true}